                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="highlight-box">
                            <p class="highlight-text">
                                <strong>{lang === 'tr' ? "Unutmayın:" : "Denken Sie daran:"}</strong> {lang === 'tr'
                                    ? "Kültürel ve sosyal programımız, öğleden sonraki öğrenme desteğimiz ve tüm öğretim materyalleri (kitaplar ve fotokopiler) kurs ücretine dahildir!"
                                    : "Unser kulturelles und soziales Programm, unsere Lernunterstützung am Nachmittag und alle Unterrichtsmaterialien (Bücher und Kopien) sind im Kurspreis enthalten!"}
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="content-right">
                    <div class="content-highlights">
                        <div class="highlight-section">
                            <div class="highlight-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>CampusGerman</h3>
                            <p>{lang === 'tr' ? "25+ yıllık deneyim ile Almanya'da Almanca öğrenmenin en iyi adresi" : "Die beste Adresse zum Deutschlernen in Deutschland mit über 25 Jahren Erfahrung"}</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="highlight-section">
                            <div class="highlight-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Küçük Gruplar' : 'Kleine Gruppen'}</h3>
                            <p>{lang === 'tr' ? "Maksimum 12 kişilik sınıflarda kişiselleştirilmiş öğrenme deneyimi" : "Personalisierte Lernerfahrung in Klassen mit maximal 12 Personen"}</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="highlight-section">
                            <div class="highlight-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>{lang === 'tr' ? 'İki Öğretmen Sistemi' : 'Zwei-Lehrer-System'}</h3>
                            <p>{lang === 'tr' ? "Her sınıfta iki öğretmen ile bireysel dil gelişimi odaklı eğitim" : "Bildung mit Fokus auf individuelle Sprachentwicklung mit zwei Lehrern in jeder Klasse"}</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="highlight-section">
                            <div class="highlight-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Esnek Başlangıç' : 'Flexibler Start'}</h3>
                            <p>{lang === 'tr' ? "Herhangi bir Pazartesi günü kursa başlayabilme imkanı" : "Möglichkeit, jeden Montag mit dem Kurs zu beginnen"}</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="highlight-section">
                            <div class="highlight-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>{lang === 'tr' ? '%98 Başarı Oranı' : '98% Erfolgsquote'}</h3>
                            <p>{lang === 'tr' ? "Kanıtlanmış başarı ile hedeflerinize ulaşın" : "Erreichen Sie Ihre Ziele mit nachgewiesenem Erfolg"}</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="highlight-section">
                            <div class="highlight-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h3>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Kültürel Program' : 'Kulturprogramm'}</h3>
                            <p>{lang === 'tr' ? "Şehir turları, spor etkinlikleri ve sosyal aktiviteler dahil" : "Stadtführungen, Sportveranstaltungen und soziale Aktivitäten inklusive"}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="contact-section">
                        <a href={`/${lang}/kontakt`} class="contact-link">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                            <span>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Hemen İletişime Geçin' : 'Jetzt Kontakt aufnehmen'}</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Kurs Kartları Section -->
    <section class="courses-section" id="kurs-kartlari">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Almanca Kurslarımız' : 'Unsere Deutschkurse'}</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Her seviyeye ve ihtiyaca uygun özel hazırlanmış kurslar' : 'Speziell entwickelte Kurse für jedes Niveau und jeden Bedarf'}</p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Filtreleme ve Arama -->
            <div class="courses-filter-section">
                <div class="filter-search-box">
                    <div class="search-wrapper">
                        <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                        <input 
                            type="text" 
                            id="courseSearchInput" 
                            placeholder={lang === 'tr' ? 'Kurs ara...' : 'Kurs suchen...'}
                        />
                        <button class="search-clear" id="searchClearBtn" style="display: none;">
                            <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="filter-buttons-row">
                    <div class="filter-btn-wrapper">
                        <button class="filter-btn" id="levelFilterBtn">
                            <span>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Dil Seviyesi' : 'Sprachniveau'}</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="filter-menu" id="levelFilterDropdown">
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="all">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Tüm Seviyeler' : 'Alle Niveaus'}</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="a1">A1</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="a2">A2</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="b1">B1</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="b2">B2</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="c1">C1</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="c2">C2</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="filter-btn-wrapper">
                        <button class="filter-btn" id="typeFilterBtn">
                            <span>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Kurs Türü' : 'Kurstyp'}</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="filter-menu" id="typeFilterDropdown">
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="all">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Tüm Kurslar' : 'Alle Kurse'}</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="yuz-yuze">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Yüz Yüze' : 'Präsenz'}</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="online">Online</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="filter-btn-wrapper">
                        <button class="filter-btn" id="periodFilterBtn">
                            <span>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Dönem' : 'Zeitraum'}</span>
                            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                        </button>
                        <div class="filter-menu" id="periodFilterDropdown">
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="all">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Tüm Dönemler' : 'Alle Zeiträume'}</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="yaz-donemi">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Yaz Dönemi' : 'Sommersemester'}</a>
                            <a href="#" class="filter-item" data-value="yil-boyu">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Yıl Boyu' : 'Ganzjährig'}</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <button class="clear-btn" id="clearFiltersBtn" style="display: none;">
                        <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
                        {lang === 'tr' ? 'Temizle' : 'Zurücksetzen'}
                    </button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="results-count" id="resultsInfo">
                    <span id="resultsCount">{anaKurslar.length}</span> {lang === 'tr' ? 'kurs bulundu' : 'Kurse gefunden'}
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="courses-grid" id="coursesGrid">
                {anaKurslar.map(kurs => {
                    // Kurs tipini belirle (filtreleme için)
                    let courseType = 'yuz-yuze';
                    let courseLevel = 'all';
                    let coursePeriod = 'yil-boyu';
                    
                    const cleanedSlug = cleanSlug(kurs.slug);
                    
                    if (cleanedSlug.startsWith('online-')) {
                        courseType = 'online';
                    }
                    
                    // Seviye belirleme
                    if (cleanedSlug.includes('-a1') || cleanedSlug.includes('a1-')) {
                        courseLevel = 'a1';
                    } else if (cleanedSlug.includes('-a2') || cleanedSlug.includes('a2-')) {
                        courseLevel = 'a2';
                    } else if (cleanedSlug.includes('-b1') || cleanedSlug.includes('b1-')) {
                        courseLevel = 'b1';
                    } else if (cleanedSlug.includes('-b2') || cleanedSlug.includes('b2-')) {
                        courseLevel = 'b2';
                    } else if (cleanedSlug.includes('-c1') || cleanedSlug.includes('c1-')) {
                        courseLevel = 'c1';
                    }
                    
                    // Dönem belirleme
                    if (cleanedSlug.includes('yaz-okulu')) {
                        coursePeriod = 'yaz-donemi';
                    }
                    
                    return (
                        <div class="course-card" data-level={`all ${courseLevel}`} data-type={courseType} data-period={coursePeriod}>
                            <div class="course-image">
                                <img src={kurs.data.image} alt={kurs.data.title}>
                            </div>
                            <div class="course-content">
                                <h3 class="course-title">{kurs.data.title}</h3>
                                <div class="course-details">
                                    {kurs.data.features.map(feature => (
                                        <div class="course-detail">
                                            <i class={feature.icon}></i>
                                            <span>{feature.description}</span>
                                        </div>
                                    ))}
                                </div>
                                <p class="course-description">
                                    {kurs.data.description}
                                </p>
                                <a href={`/${lang}/kurslar/${cleanSlug(kurs.slug)}`} class="course-btn">
                                    <span>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Detayları Gör' : 'Details ansehen'}</span>
                                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    );
                })}
            </div>
            
            <!-- Pagination -->
            <div class="pagination-wrapper" id="paginationContainer" style="display: none;">
                <div class="pagination">
                    <button class="page-btn prev" id="prevPageBtn" disabled>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
                    </button>
                    <div class="page-numbers" id="paginationNumbers"></div>
                    <button class="page-btn next" id="nextPageBtn">
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="page-info" id="paginationInfo">
                    {lang === 'tr' ? 'Sayfa' : 'Seite'} <span id="currentPageNum">1</span> / <span id="totalPagesNum">1</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Fiyatlar ve Tarihler Section -->
    <section class="pricing-dates-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Fiyatlar ve Tarihler' : 'Preise und Termine'}</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Almanca Kursları fiyatları ve başlangıç tarihleri' : 'Preise und Starttermine für Deutschkurse'}</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pricing-content">
                <!-- Akademik Almanca Kursları Fiyatları -->
                <div class="pricing-block">
                    <h3 class="pricing-block-title">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Akademik Almanca Kursları Fiyatları' : 'Preise für Akademische Deutschkurse'}</h3>
                    <div class="pricing-table-wrapper">
                        <table class="pricing-table">
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Seviye' : 'Niveau'}</th>
                                    <th>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Ders Sayısı' : 'Unterrichtsstunden'}</th>
                                    <th>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Süre' : 'Dauer'}</th>
                                    <th>{lang === 'tr' ? 'Fiyat' : 'Preis'}</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                {(['a1', 'a2', 'b1', 'b2', 'c1'] as const).map(level => {
                                    const pricing = coursePricing[lang as 'tr' | 'de'].intensive[level];
                                    return (
                                        <tr>
                                            <td><strong>{level.toUpperCase()}</strong></td>
                                            <td>{pricing.lessons}</td>
                                            <td>{pricing.duration}</td>
                                            <td><strong>{pricing.fullCourse}</strong></td>
                                        </tr>
                                    );
                                })}
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Online Kurs Fiyatları -->
                <div class="pricing-block">
                    <h3 class="pricing-block-title">{lang === 'tr' ? 'Online Almanca Kursları Fiyatları' : 'Preise für Online Deutschkurse'}</h3>
